{"type":"message","id":"75feedde","parentId":"d260f38d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:01:39.484Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c752f3a6385c41b4a3748b5a","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"AI automation agency beginner how to start first clients pricing 2024\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 8,\n  \"tookMs\": 1007,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ced36637dcd3c1a4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Start an AI Automation Agency: A Comprehensive ... - DesignRush\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ced36637dcd3c1a4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.designrush.com/agency/ai-companies/trends/how-to-start-an-ai-automation-agency\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ecfde317558e27b7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nLearn how to start and scale an AI automation agency with customized solutions, strategic pricing , and tools for long-term growth in a booming market.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"ecfde317558e27b7\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.designrush.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c0077f74ad28ee8d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Start an AI Automation Agency and Sign a Client in 7 Days\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c0077f74ad28ee8d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://altagic.com/blog/how-to-start-an-ai-automation-agency-and-sign-a-client-in-7-days/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0ef542ae5c9c04d1\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIntroduction Starting an AI automation agency from scratch and signing a high-ticket client in just 7 days may sound like a daunting challenge, but it's entirely possible with the right strategy. In