{"type":"message","id":"f29cef07","parentId":"8dcf4f18","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:06:29.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to focus on 2026-specific AI business ideas since it's now 2026 (not 2024/2025). I need to search for more current information and provide 6 beginner-friendly, profitable, easy-to-start AI business ideas that work in 2026.\n\nFrom the search results I just got, I can see several 2026-focused sources. Let me analyze them and extract the most relevant, actionable ideas for a beginner like Ivek.\n\nLooking at the results:\n1. Nucamp: Top 10 AI Business Ideas for 2026 (low-cost, high-potential)\n2. AIFirstFounders: 25 AI Business Ideas for 2026 (low startup costs)\n3. WeArePresta: 20 Profitable AI Business Ideas for 2026 (with real examples)\n4. LifeInTechMode: 30 AI Business Ideas for 2026 (profitable & scalable)\n5. Appinventiv: 20 Profitable AI Business Ideas for 2026\n6. Medium: 5 Best AI Business Ideas for Beginners in 2026\n7. Lindy.ai: 21 Practical AI Business Ideas in 2026 (low upfront cost)\n8. CEEK: Top 25 Innovative AI Business Ideas for 2026\n9. Appaca.ai: 10 Profitable AI Business Ideas for 2026\n\nI should synthesize the best beginner-friendly ideas from these 2026 sources, focusing on:\n- Easy to set up (low technical barrier)\n- High demand\n- Profitable/quick monetization\n- Beginner-friendly\n- Aligns with Ivek's skills/interests\n\nLet me extract the most promising ones from these sources.\n\nFrom the Nucamp article (first result): \"Top 10 AI Business Ideas You Can Start in 2026 (Low-Cost, High-Potential)\"\nFrom the Lindy.ai result: \"21 Practical AI Business Ideas in 2026 With Low Upfront Cost\"\nFrom the Medium article: \"The 5 Best AI Business Ideas For Beginners In 2026\"\n\nLet me get more details from some of these sources to provide specific, actionable ideas.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_